abstract: United States men's soccer team will host either Aruba or St Vincent and the Grenadines in team's opening qualifier for 2018 World Cup soccer tournament.
lead_paragraph: The United States will host either Aruba or St. Vincent and the Grenadines at Busch Stadium in St. Louis.

headline.main: First Qualifier for U.S. Will be Nov. 13
headline.print_headline: First Qualifier for U.S. Will Be Nov. 13
